    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://blog.microcode.site/en/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://blog.microcode.site/en/about/</guid>
      
        <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whatever can happen will happen.&lt;br&gt;
Some paths may seem winding, yet they are the only way to reach the horizon.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;corins-blog&#34;&gt;Corin’s Blog&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;site&#34;&gt;Site&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This site is powered by &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hugo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, built on simplicity, driven by thought.&lt;br&gt;
Every word is a record; every deployment, a renewal of ideas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here, code and words coexist: carrying both the sharpness of logic and the warmth of life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;blog&#34;&gt;Blog&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Technology isn’t the only theme here, it’s simply how I make sense of the world.&lt;br&gt;
Each post is not just a note of knowledge, but a process of self-refinement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Code can be elegant. So can life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;author&#34;&gt;Author&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A developer walking the fine line between logic and aesthetics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Believes in the power of technology, and the gentleness of time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A film lover, drawn to stories that explore the unknown and the human spirit: &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interstellar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TRON: Legacy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Finds peace in midnight stillness, and hope in the first light of dawn.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every line of code is a dialogue with the world;&lt;br&gt;
Every piece of writing, a quiet reconciliation with myself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;gratitude&#34;&gt;Gratitude&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To those who have offered help, inspiration, and understanding along the way: thank you.&lt;br&gt;
Because of you, my thoughts run deeper, and my steps grow steadier.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
